th records." J Am Med Inform Assoc 19 (2012): 735-43[4] "Product Information. Sporanox (itraconazole)." Janssen Pharmaceutica, Titusville, NJ.[5] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[6] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[7] "Product Information. Nizoral (ketoconazole)." Janssen Pharmaceutica, Titusville, NJ. (1992):[8] "Product Information. Camptosar (irinotecan)." Pharmacia and Upjohn, Kalamazoo, MI.', 1767369485);
