t (pazopanib)." GlaxoSmithKline, Research Triangle Park, NC.[2] "Product Information. Votrient (pazopanib)." GlaxoSmithKline, Research Triangle Park, NC.[3] "Product Information. Accolate (zafirlukast)." Zeneca Pharmaceuticals, Wilmington, DE.', 1767369485);
