nvolved in the N-demethylation of sildenafil." Br J Clin Pharmaacol 51 (2001): 239-48[5] Jetter A, Kinzig-Schippers M, Walchner-Bonjean M, et al. "Effects of grapefruit juice on the pharmacokinetics of sildenafil." Clin Pharmacol Ther 71 (2002): 21-29', 1767369485);
